#: ../../source/user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md:1
msgid "Environment Variables"
msgstr "环境变量"

#: ../../source/user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md:3
msgid ""
"vllm-ascend uses the following environment variables to configure the "
"system:"
msgstr "vllm-ascend 使用以下环境变量来配置系统："

#: ../../source/user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md:5
msgid ""
"**Note:** Some environment variables have been migrated to "
"`additional_config` configuration options. These environment variables "
"are still supported for backward compatibility but are marked as "
"deprecated. It is recommended to use `--additional-config` instead. See "
"[Additional Configuration](additional_config.md) for details."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** 部分环境变量已迁移至 `additional_config` 配置选项。为保持向后兼容，这些环境变量仍受支持，但已标记为弃用。建议改用 `--additional-config`。详情请参阅[附加配置](additional_config.md)。"